        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Safeguarding Coal Leasing Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the President and the Department of the Interior to obtain the approval of Congress before implementing a moratorium on coal leasing.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
